## Frontend environment variables (Vite)
## Copy this file to `frontend/ai-learning-assistant/.env.local` (or `.env`) if you need overrides.

# Base URL used by axios (should include `/v1`)
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/v1

# Base URL used to render PDF viewer links (no `/v1`)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

